paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the content validation of the ATTR Patient Symptom Survey (ATTR-PSS) for patients with ATTR amyloidosis. It mentions the TTR gene in the context of hereditary ATTR amyloidosis but does not provide specific genetic variant information.

challenges: The paper did not provide specific genetic variant information for the TTR gene.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper focused on the validation of a symptom survey and did not include genetic variant data for the TTR gene.
